Buildings

 *i386

  name:Intel 80386

  desc:Effect on updates, First level 

  cost:1 flop

  Icon:debug[0,1]
  
  on tick:yield 1 flop

  show max
  
 *i486

  name:Intel 80486

  desc:The microprocessor with great perfomance. This is Intel 80486

  cost:750 flop

  Icon:debug[1,1]
  
  on tick:yield 5 flop

  show max

Upgrades

 *386OS1

  name:Windows/386 Version 2.03

  desc:Powering Intel 80308 with increased X1.4 perfomance

  cost:3 flop

  passive:multiply yield of i386 by 1.4

  req:1 i386

  Icon:debug[2,3] debug[0,2]

 *386OS2

  name:Windows/386 Version 2.10

  desc:Powering Intel 80308 with increased X1.4 perfomance

  cost:3 flop

  passive:multiply yield of i386 by 1.4

  req:15 i386

  Icon:debug[2,3] debug[1,2]
  
Achievements

 *flopM1
 
  name:First try
  
  desc:Have <b>1 unit</b> of perfomance currency. <//><t><i><#C49814>Poor achievements earnt: </#> [poor]</i></t>
  
  req:1 flop
  
  icon:icons[0,0] icons[3,4]
  
  on earn:yield 1 ach
  on earn:yield 1 poor
  
 *flopM2
 
  name:Just before the action
  
  desc:Have <b>100 units</b> of perfomance currency. <//><t><i><#E60000>Destitute achievements earnt: </#> [destitute]</i></t>
  
  req:100 flop
  
  icon:icons[1,0] icons[3,4]
  
  on earn:yield 1 ach
  on earn:yield 1 destitute
  
 *flopM3
 
  name:Enjoy our nice work ;)
  
  desc:Have <b>1 thousand</b> of perfomance currency. <//><t><i><#FF9500>Decent achievements earnt: </#> [decent]</i></t>
  
  req:1000 flop
  
  icon:icons[2,0] icons[3,4]
  
  on earn:yield 1 ach
  on earn:yield 1 decent
  
 *flopM4
 
  name:The source of Perfomance
  
  desc:Have <b>100 thousands</b> of perfomance currency. <//><t><i><#FFFF00>Minimum achievements earnt: </#> [minimum]</i></t>
  
  req:100000 flop
  
  icon:icons[3,0] icons[3,4]
  
  on earn:yield 1 ach
  on earn:yield 1 minimum
  
 *click1
 
  name:We're just starting!
  
  desc:Clicked <b>15</b> times to boost <//><t><i><#C49814>Poor achievements earnt: </#> [poor]</i></t>
  
  req:15 boost
  
  icon:icons[0,0] icons[2,4]
  
  on earn:yield 1 ach
  on earn:yield 1 poor
  
